Omg...I'm so desperate for the tabs of this song. I tried to figure out the main riff from the video but they never did a close up on the guy playing the riff. I know the picking pattern is 4 3 2 1 2 3. The first part of the riff is:

1st finger on 4th string 2nd fret
3rd finger on 3rd string 4th fret
4th finger on 2nd string 4th fret
1st string open.

But I can't figure out what comes after that, can anyone figure it out??
